<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>秀邦の手書きメモ ― 赤澤一族 令和版</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Shippori+Mincho:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root{--bg1:#f4f4f2;--bg2:#f8f8f6;--bg3:#f2f2f0;--tx:#1a1a1a;--tx2:#555;--tx3:#999;--tx4:#bbb;--bd:rgba(0,0,0,.06);--bd2:rgba(0,0,0,.04);--glass:rgba(255,255,255,.6);--glass2:rgba(255,255,255,.7);--blur:blur(12px);--sh:0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,.03);--sh2:0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.04);--ink-grad:linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(0,0,0,.2),rgba(0,0,0,.05));--warm:rgba(245,242,235,.5);--warm-bd:rgba(140,120,80,.08);--warm-tx:#6a5a40}
*{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
body{font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;background:linear-gradient(160deg,var(--bg1),var(--bg2),var(--bg3));color:var(--tx);line-height:1.8;min-height:100vh;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased}

/* Hero compact */
.hero-compact{position:relative;overflow:hidden;padding:80px 24px 60px;text-align:center;background:linear-gradient(160deg,#2a2218,#3a3028,#2a2218);min-height:auto}
.hero-compact .ov-grain{position:absolute;inset:0;opacity:.04;background-image:url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 256 256' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='n'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='.8' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23n)'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");background-size:128px;pointer-events:none}
.hero-en{font-size:9px;letter-spacing:.5em;color:rgba(200,205,215,.25);margin-bottom:16px;animation:fi 2s ease .1s both}
.hero-title{font-family:'Shippori Mincho',serif;font-size:36px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:.2em;color:rgba(235,238,245,.85);text-shadow:0 0 60px rgba(200,205,215,.1);animation:fi 2s ease .4s both;opacity:0}
.hero-line{width:60px;height:2px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,rgba(180,185,200,.35),rgba(220,225,240,.6),rgba(180,185,200,.35),transparent);margin:18px auto;animation:fi 2s ease .7s both}
.hero-sub{font-size:12px;letter-spacing:.08em;color:rgba(200,205,215,.35);animation:fi 2s ease 1s both;line-height:2}
@keyframes fi{0%{opacity:0;transform:translateY(14px)}100%{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}}

/* Content */
.content{max-width:1000px;margin:0 auto;padding:40px 20px 60px}
.breadcrumb{font-size:12px;color:var(--tx3);margin-bottom:30px}
.breadcrumb a{color:var(--tx2);text-decoration:none}
.breadcrumb a:hover{text-decoration:underline}

/* Section headers */
.sec-head{margin:40px 0 20px}
.sec-num{font-size:10px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.15em;color:var(--tx3);margin-bottom:4px}
.sec-title{font-family:'Shippori Mincho',serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:500;color:var(--tx);letter-spacing:.06em}
.sec-line{width:100%;height:1px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(0,0,0,.12),rgba(0,0,0,.03));margin-top:10px}

/* Card */
.card{background:var(--glass);border:1px solid var(--bd2);border-radius:14px;backdrop-filter:var(--blur);box-shadow:var(--sh);padding:24px 28px;margin-bottom:18px}
.card-ink{border-left:4px solid transparent;border-image:linear-gradient(180deg,#a0a5b0,#c8cdd8,#a0a5b0) 1;border-radius:0}
.card p{font-size:14px;color:var(--tx2);line-height:2}
.card strong{color:var(--tx)}

/* Grandpa note */
.gp-note{background:rgba(245,242,235,.4);border:1px solid var(--warm-bd);border-top:2px solid #8b6914;border-radius:0 0 12px 12px;padding:18px 22px;margin:18px 0;backdrop-filter:var(--blur)}
.gp-label{font-size:10px;font-weight:600;color:#8b6914;letter-spacing:.05em;margin-bottom:6px}
.gp-note p{font-size:13px;color:var(--warm-tx);line-height:1.8}

/* Gallery grid */
.gallery{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(200px,1fr));gap:14px;margin-top:20px}
.gallery-item{position:relative;cursor:pointer;border-radius:10px;overflow:hidden;background:var(--glass);border:1px solid var(--bd2);box-shadow:var(--sh);transition:all .3s;aspect-ratio:3/4}
.gallery-item:hover{box-shadow:var(--sh2);transform:translateY(-3px)}
.gallery-item img{width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;display:block;transition:transform .3s}
.gallery-item:hover img{transform:scale(1.03)}
.gallery-item .item-label{position:absolute;bottom:0;left:0;right:0;padding:8px 12px;background:linear-gradient(transparent,rgba(0,0,0,.5));color:rgba(255,255,255,.8);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.04em;pointer-events:none}

/* Modal overlay */
.modal-overlay{display:none;position:fixed;inset:0;background:rgba(0,0,0,.85);z-index:200;justify-content:center;align-items:center;padding:20px;backdrop-filter:blur(6px)}
.modal-overlay.show{display:flex}
.modal-content{position:relative;max-width:90vw;max-height:90vh;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center}
.modal-content img{max-width:100%;max-height:80vh;object-fit:contain;border-radius:8px;box-shadow:0 4px 40px rgba(0,0,0,.3)}
.modal-close{position:fixed;top:20px;right:24px;background:none;border:none;font-size:28px;cursor:pointer;color:rgba(255,255,255,.6);width:44px;height:44px;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;transition:all .2s;z-index:210}
.modal-close:hover{background:rgba(255,255,255,.1);color:rgba(255,255,255,.9)}
.modal-nav{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:20px;margin-top:16px}
.modal-nav button{background:rgba(255,255,255,.1);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.15);color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);font-size:14px;padding:8px 18px;border-radius:8px;cursor:pointer;transition:all .2s}
.modal-nav button:hover{background:rgba(255,255,255,.2);color:#fff}
.modal-counter{font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.4);letter-spacing:.06em}

/* Page nav */
.page-nav{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;margin-top:50px;padding-top:16px;border-top:1px solid var(--bd2)}
.page-nav a{font-size:12px;color:var(--tx2);text-decoration:none}
.page-nav a:hover{color:var(--tx)}

/* Footer */
.footer{text-align:center;padding:30px 0 20px;font-size:11px;color:var(--tx4);margin-top:40px}

@media(max-width:768px){
  .hero-title{font-size:26px;letter-spacing:.15em}
  .gallery{grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(140px,1fr));gap:10px}
}
@media(max-width:600px){
  .card{padding:18px 20px}
  .gallery{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:8px}
  .gallery-item .item-label{font-size:9px;padding:6px 8px}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- Hero compact -->
<div class="hero-compact">
  <div class="ov-grain"></div>
  <div class="hero-en">AKAZAWA ICHIZOKU</div>
  <div class="hero-title">秀邦の手書きメモ</div>
  <div class="hero-line"></div>
  <div class="hero-sub">赤澤秀邦が冊子に残した調査の痕跡</div>
</div>

<!-- Content -->
<div class="content">

<div class="breadcrumb"><a href="index.html">赤澤一族 令和版</a> → 秀邦の手書きメモ</div>

<!-- Introduction -->
<div class="sec-head">
  <div class="sec-num">ABOUT</div>
  <div class="sec-title">このページについて</div>
  <div class="sec-line"></div>
</div>

<div class="card card-ink">
  <p>昭和63年（1988年）に発行された冊子「赤澤一族」には、<strong>赤澤秀邦</strong>（RIOの祖父）による赤ペンの書き込みが随所に残されている。</p>
  <br>
  <p>秀邦は晩年、各地のお寺を巡り、赤澤家のルーツを独自に調査した。その成果を冊子の余白や家系図の横に丁寧に書き加えていった。年号の補足、人物名の読み仮名、菩提寺の住所 ― 一つひとつの書き込みが、秀邦の探究心の証。</p>
  <br>
  <p>このページでは、冊子全46ページの写真を閲覧できる。各写真をクリックすると拡大表示される。</p>
</div>

<div class="gp-note">
  <div class="gp-label">秀邦の調査メモ</div>
  <p>特に家系図ページ（4〜10枚目あたり）には、赤ペンで人物名の読み仮名や官職の補足が多数書き込まれている。秀邦が冊子を何度も読み返し、自ら調べた情報を書き加えていった様子がうかがえる。</p>
</div>

<!-- Gallery -->
<div class="sec-head">
  <div class="sec-num">GALLERY</div>
  <div class="sec-title">冊子全ページ（46枚）</div>
  <div class="sec-line"></div>
</div>

